# 🛒 E-commerce Laptop Recommendation System using Machine Learning

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is an **E-commerce Laptop Recommendation System** developed as part of **Mission 2** of the Machine Learning Internship. The system recommends laptops based on their specifications using machine learning techniques. It helps users discover similar products by analyzing laptop features and generating personalized recommendations.

The project demonstrates the implementation of:

- Content-Based Filtering
- Collaborative Filtering
- Hybrid Recommendation System
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Feature Engineering
- Model Evaluation

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Clean and preprocess laptop data.
- Perform Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA).
- Extract useful features from laptop specifications.
- Build a Content-Based Recommendation System using TF-IDF and Cosine Similarity.
- Implement Collaborative Filtering using Singular Value Decomposition (SVD).
- Develop a Hybrid Recommendation System by combining both approaches.
- Evaluate the recommendation model using standard metrics.

---

## 📂 Dataset

**Dataset Name:** Laptop Price Dataset

The dataset contains **1303 laptop records** with the following attributes:

- Company
- Product
- TypeName
- Inches
- ScreenResolution
- CPU
- RAM
- Memory
- GPU
- Operating System
- Weight
- Price (Euros)

